      "module_path": "task_contract",
      "docs": "Outcome of the `bin/sotp task-contract coverage` verification. Passed: every canonical layer signal document is available, all catalogue entries are attributed to at least one task, all attributed entries exist in the catalogue, and every task key in task-contract.json exists in impl-plan.json. Blocked carries the list of coverage violations (MissingTaskContract, OrphanEntry, InvalidEntryRef, MissingSignalDocument, InvalidTaskRef). The Blocked variant is #[non_exhaustive]. Use CoverageVerifyOutcome::blocked() to construct a Blocked outcome so the non-empty invariant is checked.",
      "spec_refs": [
