      "module_path": "tddd::catalogue",
      "docs": "Per-type signal evaluation result: the confidence signal for one catalogue entry, derived from the 3-way diff (catalogue declaration / merged baseline / live scanned code). Element type of TypeSignalsDocument. This modify entry records the addition of is_unknown_kind(), an encapsulation helper that keeps the 'unknown' kind-tag detection inside the domain layer. The pre-review gate (IN-04) JOINs impl_catalog signals with entry keys; synthetic report-only rows (kind_tag = 'unknown') must be excluded from this JOIN, and is_unknown_kind() provides the predicate without leaking the string literal into usecase callers.",
      "spec_refs": [
        { "file": "track/items/pre-review-task-contract-conformance-gate-2026-06-27/spec.json", "anchor": "IN-04" }
      ],
